videos.description: Miles Bridges drives and hits tough layup while getting fouled to create 3-point play.
videos.headline: MSU's Bridges hits tough layup, draws foul

videos.description: Tom Izzo tells Molly McGrath that his star player Miles Bridges wasn't playing good enough defense in the first half against Iowa.
videos.headline: Izzo critical of Spartans defense

videos.description: Miles Bridges drives down the baseline and nails the reverse layup.
videos.headline: MSU's Bridges sinks impressive reverse layup

videos.description: Tyler Cook takes the inside pass from Isaiah Moss and throws down a dunk that gives the Hawkeyes the lead.
videos.headline: Cook's slam fires up Iowa crowd

videos.description: Jordan Bohannon ends up on the ground after hitting 3-pointer that extends Iowa's lead.
videos.headline: Iowa's Bohannon sinks 3 while falling

videos.description: Kenny Goins gives the Spartans the lead after getting a friendly bounce on a wide-open 3.
videos.headline: MSU's Goins gets friendly roll on 3

videos.description: Tom Izzo tells Molly McGrath that while his team did some good things they still did dumb things in their win against Iowa.
videos.headline: Izzo: 'we can't put together a full game yet'
